Add Raster Layer
➜ Layer → Add Raster → Christchurch Topo50 map.tif

Build Image Pyramids
➜ Right-click layer → Properties → Pyramids
➜ Select all resolutions → Build pyramids → OK

Set Snapping
➜ Settings → Options → Digitizing
➜ Default snap mode: Vertex and Segment

Create Spatialite Layer
➜ Layer → Add Spatialite Layer
➜ Create DB: MySpatialDataBase.sqlite
➜ Layer name: Digitized_Road | Geometry: Line | CRS: EPSG 4167
➜ Add fields: Name, Class

Start Digitizing
➜ Toggle Editing → Add Feature
➜ Click to add vertices along roads
➜ Right-click to finish → Enter Name & Class
➜ Save edits! ✅
